    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. The exterior has significant paint fading, several deep dents, and visible rust spots on the wheel arches. Mechanically, the engine runs but requires immediate attention for a persistent oil leak and a suspension that needs a complete overhaul. The interior shows heavy wear, including tears in the upholstery and non-functional air conditioning. This would be an ideal project car or a source for parts for someone with the right mechanical skills.",
