    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This FD3S RX-7 is a benchmark example featuring the legendary 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine. The drivetrain maintains factory-spec compression across all rotor faces, delivering linear boost through the transition phase without oscillation. The chassis is structurally immaculate, retaining its original double-wishbone suspension geometry and Torsen limited-slip differential for surgical handling precision. Every vacuum line, heat shield, and cooling component is in concours-level condition, free from the typical thermal degradation found in lesser examples. A truly turn-key investment for the discerning collector.",
